sub_title: Software Engineer at KIOS Research and Innovation Center of Excellence
summary: My name is Stylianos Filippou, I received my B.Eng in Computer Engineering from the Department of Electrical and Computer Engineering at the University of Cyprus in 2017 and my MSc Degree in Artificial Intelligence from Utrecht University in 2019. By the end of my Bachelor Studies i had the opportunity to join Huawei’s Summer School, titled “Seeds for the future”, that took place at Huawei’s headquarters in China. In 2018, i gained an internship position at Utrecht University to work on smart traffic networks. In February 2020 I joined KIOS Center of Excellence as a software engineer and since then I am working on multiple research and innovation hub projects.
